c function is advisable.', 'Synergism', 'The use of naltrexone with other potentially hepatotoxic agents should be avoided whenever possible (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/37864/', '', 'Tinidazole, Tetracycline, Cefepime, Norfloxacin, Ciprofloxacin, Metronidazole, Cefuroxime, Secnidazole, Cefixime, Amikacin, Ofloxacin, More', 'Oxymorphone, Tapentadol, Butorphanol, Dezocine, Opium, Pentazocine, Nalbuphine, Dihydrocodeine, Naloxone, Codeine, Nalmefene, More', 1767369485);
